{"type":null,"faqId":33348,"title":"为什么使用放大手势时，触摸屏反应慢/不灵敏？","answer":" <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n <style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n </style>\n <div>\n <p>\n <span>开启放大手势功能后，通过三击屏幕可以放大或缩小屏幕内容方便操作，但目前此功能设计与用户习惯可能不完全匹配，可能会造成触摸屏不灵敏的错觉。 </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n <span>若要取消放大手势功能，请点击设置-辅助功能-放大手势，关闭“放大手势”开关。 </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n <img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105415\" style=\"width:2.1840277in;height:3.8868055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"> <img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105416\" style=\"width:2.1868055in;height:3.8916667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"> <img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=105417\" style=\"width:2.1888888in;height:3.8909721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"> </p>\n <p>\n <span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。 </span>\n </p>\n </div>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7950","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748585000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":14,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"放大手势,反应慢","avgScore":0.0,"createDate